title: Aavegotchi support on Opensea.
body: Opensea is much larger and easier to use by the general population than Aavegotchis marketplace. By integrating it, we will simplify the onboarding process for many users. Trading fees can still be redirected to the DAO.
author: 0x9875094945893d40979E2858B6cAf788dcCE3368
